{
  "stem": "25809.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no communication.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- literally, my sister was there, and she and I, we were on our own.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it is-- it was interesting how my sister was kind of on her own and stayed very privately and how I stayed very privately.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- we just literally played it cool, and we didn't want to draw attention to ourselves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- we stayed very quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't want anybody to know we were there, basically speaking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- as a matter of fact, a few years in the war, I started getting dreams.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the dreams actually became nightmares.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That followed me, until I came to a-- and still they happen from time to time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I resolved my nightmares, actually, for 90% in-- when I moved to Australia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I did have regular nightmares of being in an area and feeling myself like sinking through the ground, or I'd be in the water and sinking down, or in a swamp or anything, it was-- or in a tree, falling out of a tree.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was always this moment where I had a feeling that I was being sucked down or sucked under or disappearing through the ground.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Could be a forest, could be anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I would wake up, and I would say, OK, and I would fall asleep again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I had nightmares on a continuous basis, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Though those nightmares still plague me, but I can deal with them now much better, because I know what caused them, and I found that out in Australia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was-- but I might be getting ahead of-- losing track of everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I-- when I moved to Australia, I came to live with-- with a Dr. van der Portens, where I had rented a room.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
